titles.title: A resolution to authorize the printing of additional copies of a Senate report entitled "Developments in Aging: 1993".

action.text: Referred to the Committee on Rules.

calendar.text: Committee on Rules. Ordered to be reported without amendment favorably.

action.text: Committee on Rules. Reported to Senate by Senator Ford without amendment. Without written report.

calendar.text: Placed on Senate Legislative Calendar under General Orders. Calendar No. 463.

vote.text: Resolution agreed to in Senate without amendment by Voice Vote.

bill.summary: 3/25/1994--Introduced. Authorizes the printing of additional copies of the annual report of the Special Committee on Aging to the Senate, entitled "Developments in Aging: 1993."
